interpretation.irrigable_now: Meets scope_alignment=YES, added_value=YES, consumer_ready=YES, and has Signalt source; plus stage has equipped/operational consumers.
interpretation.not_irrigable_yet: Row meets hard requirements but stage lacks equipped consumer coverage (based on declarations/registrations).
interpretation.definitely_not: Fails at least one hard requirement (scope coherence, value-add, via signals, or consumer readiness) under current artifacts.
